985
02:03:20,018 --> 02:03:25,397
<i>Runs up into the sky</i>

986
02:03:25,690 --> 02:03:30,068
<i>A gently swaying, misty haze</i>

987
02:03:30,903 --> 02:03:35,407
<i>Surrounding and holding</i>

988
02:03:35,700 --> 02:03:41,413
<i>Unnoticed by anyone, all alone</i>

989
02:03:42,206 --> 02:03:47,419
<i>Soaring upwards</i>

990
02:03:47,879 --> 02:03:52,591
<i>Not afraid of anything</i>

991
02:03:52,884 --> 02:03:58,221
<i>Dancing up</i>

992
02:03:58,556 --> 02:04:03,769
<i>Longing to be in the sky</i>

993
02:04:04,062 --> 02:04:09,608
<i>Speeding through the sky</i>

994
02:04:10,068 --> 02:04:20,118
<i>A whole life, a vapor trail</i>

995
02:04:21,079 --> 02:04:25,791
<i>Even before dying</i>

996
02:04:26,959 --> 02:04:32,297
<i>From that window, up high</i>

997
02:04:32,590 --> 02:04:37,135
<i>Watching the sky</i>

998
02:04:37,929 --> 02:04:42,307
<i>Now no one understands</i>

999
02:04:42,934 --> 02:04:48,313
<i>No one would understand</i>

1000
02:04:49,607 --> 02:04:59,825
<i>All they could think was...
"Too young"</i>

1001
